  "title": "Tech Sales Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Lead Generation & Management:</strong> Sourcing, qualifying, and managing potential clients (leads).</li><li><strong>Product Demonstrations:</strong> Conducting technical presentations and demos to showcase product value, often translating complex jargon into business benefits.</li><li><strong>Relationship Building:</strong> Establishing and maintaining long-term relationships with clients.</li><li><strong>Negotiation & Closing:</strong> Handling objections, negotiating contracts, and closing sales to meet targets.</li><li><strong>Market Research:</strong> Analyzing client needs and staying updated on the latest technology trends.</li><li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Preparing proposals, tenders, and sales reports. </li></ul>",
